      "groupIds": [
        "type_1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 36=2²×3², 48=2⁴×3¹\nStep 2: Common primes with LOWEST power\n  2²(min of 2,4) and 3¹(min of 2,1)\nStep 3: HCF = 2²×3 = 4×3 = 12\n\nTRICK (factor tree):\n       36           48\n      / \\          / \\\n     2  18        2  24\n       / \\          / \\\n      2   9        2  12\n         / \\         / \\\n        3   3       2   6\n                       / \\\n                      2   3\n\nCommon: 2²×3 = 12\n\nAnswer: HCF = 12 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
