    {
      "id": "el_60",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1861,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: N÷6, N÷9, N÷12 all give rem 5\n  So N-5 is divisible by 6, 9, and 12\nStep 2: N-5 = LCM(6,9,12) = 36\n  N = 36+5 = 41\n\nTRICK (same remainder rule):\nN = LCM(divisors) + R\n= LCM(6,9,12) + 5 = 36+5 = 41\n\n  ┌─────────────────────────┐\n  │  N-5 divisible by all   │\n  │  N-5 = LCM = 36        │\n  │  N = 41                 │\n  └─────────────────────────┘\n\nVerify: 41/6=6r5✓ 41/9=4r5✓ 41/12=3r5✓\n\nAnswer: Smallest number = 41 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6000,
      "version": 1,
